BACKGROUND: Older adults (OA) with advanced cancer (AC) undergoing phase I 
clinical trials (PICT) have poor prognosis. There are no studies which describe 
symptoms experienced by OA.
METHODS: Retrospective chart review of PICT participants >60 years. OA were 
